				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Etched Bone Spike vs. Battle Drummer's Main-Gauche<a name="32625"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 2 04 8:52 PM</span></td>
