			<tr>
				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Etched Bone Spike vs. Battle Drummer's Main-Gauche<a name="33166"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 6 04 11:28 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>In this case, whether you go by raw ratio or straight fastest delay - the answer is the same -- the Battle Drummer's Main Gauche.  The Allakhazam efficiency ratings are separated into the basic eff. rating (primary hand) and a secondary hand efficiency rating which removes the bonus damage from the equation.  In other words, it compensates for that whole ratio vs. raw speed issue and goes by actual DPS produced.  It does NOT factor in proc damage or increased attack due to weapon stats -- consequently, a weapon with vengence 2 or something like that or a big proc like the Sceptre of Destruction's anarchy proc, would have to be evaluated for that sort of damage separately.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="SmallText"><hr size="1" align="left" width="15%"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=443370">Steppy Astravox</a><br>
Code of Silence<br>
